                        </summary>
                        <div class="expandable-body">
                            <div class="detail-grid">
                                <div class="detail-block">
                                    <h4 class="detail-block-title">Architecture</h4>
                                    <ul class="detail-list">
                                        <li><strong>Log Collection:</strong> gRPC ingestion (unary + streaming) with REST API fallback,
                                            structured logging format for .NET application integration</li>
                                        <li><strong>Storage &amp; Indexing:</strong> Elasticsearch with index rotation, retention management,
                                            and query optimization for TB-scale data</li>
                                        <li><strong>Buffering:</strong> Redis for reliable log delivery — cannot lose production logs</li>
                                        <li><strong>No Kafka</strong> — direct ingestion to Elasticsearch (intentional architectural decision)</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                <div class="detail-block">
                                    <h4 class="detail-block-title">Technical Challenges Solved</h4>
                                    <ul class="detail-list">
                                        <li><strong>Scale:</strong> Efficient indexing strategies and query optimization for 3TB+ daily volume</li>
                                        <li><strong>Performance:</strong> gRPC streaming for high throughput with batching and backpressure handling</li>
                                        <li><strong>Reliability:</strong> Idempotent ingestion, retry mechanisms, Redis buffering for zero log loss</li>
                                        <li><strong>Data Model:</strong> Unified log schema with field mapping and metadata standardization across 300+ services</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="detail-block" style="margin-top:1rem;">
                                <h4 class="detail-block-title">Business Value</h4>
                                <p class="detail-note">
                                    Centralized logging for the entire ecosystem. Reduced mean time to detect from <strong>hours to minutes</strong>.
                                    Single source of truth for debugging production issues.
                                    <strong>Master's thesis</strong> based on 2 years of real production data — a rare combination of academic rigor
                                    and production validation.
                                </p>
                            </div>
